        </div>
        {{>form}}

        <div class="overview">
            <h1><b><b>Overview</b></b></h1><br>
            <p>
                A Business Development Analyst (BDA) is a key player in driving the growth and success of a company.
                BDAs are analytical professionals who possess a deep understanding of market dynamics, industry trends,
                and customer needs. They play a crucial role in identifying and evaluating new business opportunities
                for the organization.
            </p>

            <br><br>
            <b>
