            <h1><b><b>Course Curriculum</b></b></h1>
            <br>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            <strong> Business Fundamentals</strong>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            BDA courses typically start by providing a solid foundation in core business concepts. This
                            includes topics such as business strategy, marketing principles, financial analysis, market
                            research, and organizational behavior. Understanding these fundamentals is crucial for
                            effective business development analysis.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            <strong>Market Analysis and Research </strong>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            BDAs need to be proficient in conducting market analysis and research to identify potential
                            opportunities. BDA courses cover various research methodologies, data collection techniques,
                            and analysis tools. Students learn how to gather and interpret market data, evaluate
                            industry trends, and assess competitor activities to make informed business decisions.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            <strong> Business Strategy</strong>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Developing effective business strategies is a central focus of a BDA course. Students learn
                            how to assess market potential, analyze competitive landscapes, and formulate strategies
                            that align with organizational goals. Strategic planning, SWOT analysis, and strategic
                            implementation techniques are covered to equip individuals with the skills needed to drive
                            business growth.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                            <strong>Relationship Building and Negotiation</strong>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            BDAs play a crucial role in building and managing relationships with clients, partners, and
                            stakeholders. BDA courses often emphasize effective communication, networking, and
                            negotiation skills. Students learn strategies for relationship building, effective
                            communication techniques, and negotiation tactics to foster successful collaborations and
                            partnerships.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                            <strong>Data Analysis and Decision Making</strong>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            BDA courses typically include training in data analysis and decision-making techniques.
                            Students learn how to use statistical tools, data visualization techniques, and analytical
                            frameworks to derive meaningful insights from data. This enables them to make data-driven
                            decisions and recommendations that contribute to business growth.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSix">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            <strong>Project Management</strong>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Business development initiatives often involve managing projects from inception to
                            completion. BDA courses may include project management principles and methodologies.
                            Students learn project planning, resource allocation, risk management, and monitoring
                            techniques to successfully execute business development projects.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSeven">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                            <strong>Professional Development</strong>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSeven"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            BDA courses may also focus on developing professional skills necessary for a successful
                            career in business development. These can include presentation skills, teamwork, leadership,
                            and critical thinking. Ethical considerations and business ethics are also emphasized to
                            ensure responsible and ethical business practices.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
